# -*- mode: snippet -*-
# name: dotnet format
# key: .nFMT
# In order to work you need to run first:
# - dotnet tool install -g dotnet-format
# - be sure to have the tool into the path ($HOME/.dotnet/tools)
# - add the `.editorconfig` file at the root of the .net project in order to
#   automatically remove the unused imports (https://github.com/dotnet/format/blob/main/docs/Supported-.editorconfig-options.md)
# --

dotnet format --fix-style warn